05?irgwc=1&amp;utm_source=2862475-NME%20Networks%20Media%20Limited&amp;utm_medium=affiliate&amp;utm_campaign=2862475&amp;awtrc=&amp;clickId=RKUTRgyekxyPW0Hxo00WPWwaUkFS0GV3iX3SU00&amp;camefrom=CFC_BUYAT_2862475&amp;ircid=7559" target="_blank" rel="noopener">您可以在此处找到任何剩余的门票（英国/爱尔兰）</a> 。</p><p>德克兰·麦肯纳 (Declan McKenna) 明年还将出席<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/trnsmt-2024-liam-gallagher-gerry-cinmamon-calvin-harris-lead-line-up-3545593">TRNSMT 音乐节</a>和利兹现场：公园演出。</p></div><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/declan-mckenna-releases-new-single-elevator-hum-listen-3552137">聆听 Declan McKenna 阳光亲吻的新单曲“Elevator Hum”的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
