></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/bam-margera-rips-into-jackass-cast-in-bizarre-music-video-3472643">巴姆·马格拉 (Bam Margera)</a>表示，在经历了药物滥用和成瘾史后，他已经清醒 100 天了。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：</strong> <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/uncharted-review-tom-holland-3158893"><strong>《神秘海域》评论：汤姆·赫兰德的地图外冒险失去了情节</strong></a></li></ul><p>这位曾主演 MTV 真人秀特技节目《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/jackass"><em>Jackass》</em></a>的前特技演员一直公开讲述自己的毒瘾经历，分享自己接受了为期一年的毒品和酒精治疗计划，并于今年 4 月在 Instagram 上发布了一条帖子，宣称自己会“戒酒”。</p><p>马格拉表示，他的儿子菲尼克斯是这一决定背后的灵感来源，他写道：“为了狼菲尼克斯的缘故。今天是我戒酒的日子。”</p><p>马格拉现在宣布他已经戒酒 100 天，并将这部分归功于好莱坞明星<a href="https://www.nme.com/en_au/news/film/mark-wahlberg-on-eating-11000-calories-a-day-to-play-boxing-priest-it-wasnt-fun-2998389">马克·沃尔伯格</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3552138" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3552138" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3552138" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Mark-Wahlberg.jpg" alt="马克·沃尔伯格" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Mark-Wahlberg.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Mark-Wahlberg-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Mark-Wahlberg-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Mark-Wahlberg-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Mark-Wahlberg-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Mark-Wahlberg-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3552138" class="wp-caption-text">马克·沃尔伯格于 2023 年 11 月 14 日在内华达州拉斯维加斯。图片来源：Getty/摄影：Greg Doherty/Getty Images for Netflix © 2023</figcaption></figure><p>据<a href="https://www.unilad.com/celebrity/news/jackass-bam-margera-100-days-sober-825804-20231201" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Unilad 报道</em></a>，马格拉还称赞健身房帮助他专注于自己的清醒之路，并表示他和女友丹妮每天都锻炼身体。他还透露，他会在贴满沃尔伯格照片的健身房里锻炼。</p><p>这个想法来自健身房老板贾里德·泰勒 (Jarred Taylor)，他在战争电影<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/reviews-explosions-in-the-sky-15446-307410"><em>《孤独的幸存者</em></a>》(2013) 中与沃尔伯格密切合作后，用<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/robert-de-niro-turned-down-martin-scorseses-the-departed-gangs-of-new-york-3444377"><em>《无间行者</em></a>》演员电影中的剧照装饰了健身房。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C0M3-R9vyPz/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.6